    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 16,
    "text": "And the Jebusite, and the Amorite, and the Girgasite,",
    "hash": "3031379e539371ad93a8b460817ebac80fe3ed98239ffce6ef74594742f4e66d"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.17",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 17,
    "text": "And the Hivite, and the Arkite, and the Sinite,",
    "hash": "7af4cbf3460c5ee3d9ad349593ef72b0e845016721f96cd7b4c15ca542ca20d9"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.18",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 18,
    "text": "And the Arvadite, and the Zemarite, and the Hamathite: and afterward were the families of the Canaanites spread abroad.",
