  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.19",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 19,
    "text": "And the border of the Canaanites was from Sidon, as thou comest to Gerar, unto Gaza; as thou goest, unto Sodom, and Gomorrah, and Admah, and Zeboim, even unto Lasha. {Gaza: Heb. Azzah}",
    "hash": "f7a90ed788113ce63ac790c58c03f818c2197077ce532a8b1052572cf7431ab9"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.20",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 20,
    "text": "These {are} the sons of Ham, after their families, after their tongues, in their countries, {and} in their nations.",
    "hash": "22e1f4484e1b45cc05729556fa057b57f1b5d9ac822040376078fe9b08949d10"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.21",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 21,
    "text": "Unto Shem also, the father of all the children of Eber, the brother of Japheth the elder, even to him were {children} born.",
    "hash": "cbd2d9ad7cb3daaae365425a34f2397615ca56123de7c8e86aa389fa406cdd3a"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.22",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 22,
    "text": "The children of Shem; Elam, and Asshur, and Arphaxad, and Lud, and Aram. {Arphaxad: Heb. Arpachshad}",
    "hash": "b56cf4da6ba052f5ad9c4a66bdbaa4c313c6180eef20bde3d92cc94912dfb2f5"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.23",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 23,
    "text": "And the children of Aram; Uz, and Hul, and Gether, and Mash.",
    "hash": "56abc0e1ea21690cdfb4e1ad71fbac269df32cc329555a8bbda270834910996d"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.24",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 24,
    "text": "And Arphaxad begat Salah; and Salah begat Eber. {Salah: Heb. Shelah}",
    "hash": "3fb5ebdb0c2db9ffcbfb2a07d333e5e1c1eec6231f8d904f4ef1977b4d386d17"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.25",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 25,
    "text": "And unto Eber were born two sons: the name of one {was} Peleg; for in his days was the earth divided; and his brother's name {was} Joktan. {Peleg: that is Division}",
    "hash": "cbdf8ccdee461fa01e65dd5da26fe1c0909a386c1e38e4712e1a8026bf2fddd3"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.26",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 26,
    "text": "And Joktan begat Almodad, and Sheleph, and Hazarmaveth, and Jerah,",
    "hash": "c4d308c46b0fdd1f59b3abe0dd05429ec42f65dda31b41e75cd723e43621056c"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.27",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 27,
    "text": "And Hadoram, and Uzal, and Diklah,",
    "hash": "7cba0cb073f613cfbc4dcec795476f31a9820a2b381f11f603be08c500db6258"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.28",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 28,
    "text": "And Obal, and Abimael, and Sheba,",
    "hash": "26a81e36adffbc9446e8d7916504684f82fc8e6da5ecb95410f9ee487825aaac"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.29",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 29,
    "text": "And Ophir, and Havilah, and Jobab: all these {were} the sons of Joktan.",
    "hash": "fd4dc9a32b8e1505cfc56f765b7261cf1d670b643fefc99c5179e59073a8e4b6"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.30",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 30,
    "text": "And their dwelling was from Mesha, as thou goest unto Sephar a mount of the east.",
    "hash": "8f423f8e4684dedd86a2f2cfdab0f43be7fc68c8ec172b16c69e414105a7d86a"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.31",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 31,
    "text": "These {are} the sons of Shem, after their families, after their tongues, in their lands, after their nations.",
    "hash": "06983841b244497881ac111973faf560c03d0c7fe3d7378ac859adab57009bdb"
  },
  {
    "id": "GEN.10.32",
    "book": "Genesis",
    "bookNum": 1,
    "bookAbbrev": "GEN",
    "chapter": 10,
    "verse": 32,
    "text": "These {are} the families of the sons of Noah, after their generations, in their nations: and by these were the nations divided in the earth after the flood.",
    "hash": "5768d2f6a322e0e70b6b310eaf0bd670c0db8bfd6f056a8e602ecc08c3144ea5"
  }
]